      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used under institutional software QA protocol. Version-controlled solver with regression test suite covering turbulence and scalar-transport modules. Achieved Gradation 2 exceeds MRL 2 requirement of Gradation 1."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
