      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; Gradation 1 sufficient.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal equivalency mapping between simulation inputs and physical test parameters is not required. Boundary conditions (inlet velocity profiles, outlet pressure) set to match measured values within 2%. Gradation 1 accepted."
    }
